<item>
            <title>[FLINK-38108] Incorrect conversion from Java BigDecimal to SQL DECIMAL</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-38108</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Table API
&lt;/span&gt;tableEnv.fromValues(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;0.011&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)).printSchema();
&amp;gt; DECIMAL(5, 3) NOT NULL

&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// SQL
&lt;/span&gt;tableEnv.executeSql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SELECT TYPEOF(0.011)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).print();
&amp;gt; DECIMAL(4, 3) NOT NULL
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue is caused by incorrect precision conversion in the Table API.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By the way, this issue has been discussed before, but the actions taken did not resolve the problem. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-36378&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;FLINK-36378&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
